{"tid":1744662,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"點睇理大學生呢頭話自己反中，果頭又話想食大陸海底撈？","createTime":"2019-11-22T00:34:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-24T07:22:32.000Z","uid":57405,"like":34,"dislike":139,"uniUserReply":80,"replies":[{"pid":"d93dfd10ce357d0045ebdbe4c9f1f72ae77bce39","tid":1744662,"uid":57405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T00:34:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/63XVbkY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F63XVbkY.jpg&h=57282277&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n//昨日有傳媒錄得片段，差佬用大聲公在理工門外進行廣播，聲稱留守理工者「好可憐」「只可以食冷冰冰嘅生命麵包」， 而差佬就可以「上深圳食海底撈哈哈」。<br />\n<br />\n「生命麵包。」死差佬説。<br />\n<br />\n「生命麵包」這名字由來是這樣的。<br />\n60年代，香港還是一個為飽腹發愁、缺乏營養認知的時代，嘉頓開闢了在麵包中加入維他命和礦物質的先河，希望更多人借食用麵包補充營養素，所以取名「生命麵包」。 70年代幾次天災，政府都以生命麵包作為主要賑災食物，派發于流離失所人士，協助他們渡過生死難關。<br />\n那麽，留守者的餐單上配有「在香港本土史上多次伴同香港人對抗命運」的生命麵包，不是理所當然的事嗎?<br />\n<br />\n傳送門：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10220425056486586&amp;set=gm.10156371821110286&amp;type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphoto.php%3Ffbid%3D10220425056486586%26set%3Dgm.10156371821110286%26type%3D3%26theater&d=t5TWSf1rAjisfLcmnBMt80yCzF7GSvQxQofikz39bzk%3D&h=ecfa197c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10220425056486586&amp;set=gm.10156371821110286&amp;type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n說好的「抵制中國」呢？"},{"pid":"246f1a3fa48c8909a438c69c2087b9645a4b64ae","tid":1744662,"uid":47614,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T00:35:03.000Z","msg":"分化post"},{"pid":"5a8ed856c812fdab83b2d9609420ba3d03eaa6f4","tid":1744662,"uid":997,"like":44,"dislike":0,"score":44,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T00:35:36.000Z","msg":"你up乜撚呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"310778181fd018a85b1f08c720cdf3a23db8eb79","tid":1744662,"uid":125026,"like":54,"dislike":1,"score":53,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T00:35:37.000Z","msg":"警甴話想食海底撈，關理大人咩事"},{"pid":"0